    (h‚ÇÅf‚ÇÇ : MeromorphicOn f‚ÇÇ Set.univ) (h‚ÇÇf‚ÇÇ : ‚àÄ z ‚àà univ, meromorphicOrderAt f‚ÇÇ z ‚â† ‚ä§) :
